<placeName cert="high">Philadelphia</placeName></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><div n="r" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Πετοβάστις Ζήνωνι χαίρειν. γέγ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ραφ</supplied>ά σοι πλε<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ο</supplied>νάκις περί μ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ου</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὅ</unclear>πως ἂν <choice><corr>γράψηις</corr><sic>γραψεις</sic></choice> Ἑρμαφίλωι 

    <lb n="2"/>ἵνα <sic>με</sic> διῆταί <add place="supralinear">με</add> ἐκ τῆς φυλακῆς· σὺ <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">δὲ κα</supplied>τε<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ρ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ρα</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">θ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ύ</unclear>μηκας, καὶ ταῦτα ἔργων ἡμῖν ἐνεστηκότων. 

    <lb n="3"/>ὑπελάμβανον οὖν σε μὴ οὕτως ε<gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/><gap extent="5" reason="lost" unit="character"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ε</supplied>ιν, <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἀλλὰ</supplied> τὴν πᾶσαν σπουδὴν περί μου <add place="supralinear"><choice><corr>ποιήσεσθαι</corr><sic>ποησεσθαι</sic></choice>·</add> ὁ γὰρ Ἑρ-

    <lb n="4"/>μάφιλος οὔ φησιν ἀφήσειν με, ἐὰν μὴ σὺ α<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὐ</supplied>τῶι <choice><corr>γράψηις</corr><sic>γ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ρ</unclear>αψεις</sic></choice>. πολλάκις γὰρ αὐτῶι ἀπέσταλκα 

    <lb n="5"/>ὑπομνήματα. γίνωσκε δὲ διότι οὐ πρὸς ὀφείλημα ἀπῆγμαι· τὰ γὰρ δίκαια <choice><corr>πεποίηκα</corr><sic>πεποηκα</sic></choice> τῶι βα-

    <lb n="6"/>σιλεῖ. σὺ οὖν καλῶς ἂν <choice><corr>ποιήσαις</corr><sic>ποησαις</sic></choice> <choice><corr>γράψας</corr><sic>γραψαις</sic></choice> αὐτῶι ἐπιστολὴν ἵνα ἀφεθῶ· ὡσαύτως δὲ καὶ Πύθωνι 

    <lb n="7"/>καὶ Ἀντιπάτρωι γράψον αὐτοῖς ἵνα μνησθῶσιν αὐτῶι ἅμα τῆι <subst><add place="inline">ἐπιστολῆι</add><del rend="corrected">επιστολης</del></subst> <subst><add place="inline">τῆι</add><del rend="corrected">της</del></subst> παρὰ σοῦ ἀποδιδομέ-

    <lb n="8"/>νηι αὐτῶι. ἠξίωσα δὲ καὶ Νικαίαν ἀποδημῆσαι πρὸς σέ, ὅπως ἂν αὐτῶι <choice><corr>δῶις</corr><sic>δοις</sic></choice> ἐπιστολὴν πρὸς Ἑρ-

    <lb n="9"/>μάφιλον· λέγουσιν γὰρ αὐτὸν <subst><add place="inline">μέλλειν</add><del rend="corrected">εελλειν</del></subst> ἐγδημεῖν εἰς Μέμφιν.   ἔρρωσο. 
</ab></div><div n="v" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="19"/>Ζήνω<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">νι</supplied>. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.1134" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.1134" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="-0241" notBefore="-0248" type="textDate">248 - 241 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.1134" part="N" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Zur Datierung vgl. BL IX, S. 54.</p></div><div n="meta.1134" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Cair. Zen.</title><biblScope type="volume">3</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">59496</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">1134</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0092</series>; <biblScope type="volume">3</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">59496</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0092;3;59496" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.1134" part="N" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><bibl type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">IX</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">54</biblScope></bibl></div><div n="meta.1134" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p><bibl type="illustration">Pl. XXVII</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.1134" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><placeName cert="high" type="ancientFindspot">Krokodilopolis</placeName> (<geogName cert="high" type="nome">Arsinoites</geogName>), <geogName cert="high" key="Aegyptus" type="ancientRegion">Egypt</geogName></p></div><div n="meta.1134" part="N" type="figure"><p><figure href="http://ipap.csad.ox.ac.uk/4DLink4/4DACTION/IPAPwebquery?vPub=P.Cair.Zen.&amp;vVol=3&amp;vNum=59496"><figDesc>Abbildung im Internet</figDesc></figure></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>